'''Hydroponic vats''' or '''hydroponic tanks''' were used to house and grow various types of plants and spices.

The [[Yuuzhan Vong]] used hydroponic vats on their [[Starship/Legends|starships]] to house [[villip]]s. On [[Jubilar/Legends|Jubilar]], [[Miagi Baker]] grew [[Jandarra]] in dozens of hydroponic tanks, kept in a hydroponic warehouse, around [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]].

In [[43 ABY]] on [[Dorin/Legends|Dorin]] [[Kel Dor/Legends|Kel Dor]] [[Hidden Ones]] had some hydroponic vats, where various [[Vegetable/Legends|vegetables]] and [[Grain/Legends|grains]] were grown inside their [[Caverns of the Hidden One|caverns]].

